{{Youmay|the Director of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Republic Senate's]] [[Senate Bureau of Intelligence/Legends|intelligence service]]|the [[Director of Republic Intelligence|Director]] of the [[Republic Military/Legends|Republic Military's]] [[Republic Intelligence/Legends|intelligence service]]}}
The '''Director of the Senate Bureau of Intelligence''', also known as the '''Director-General of the Senate Bureau of Intelligence''', was the head of the [[Senate Bureau of Intelligence/Legends|Senate Bureau of Intelligence]]. The SBI was an organization of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Senate]] and was separate from its [[Republic Military/Legends|military]] counterpart, [[Republic Intelligence/Legends|Republic Intelligence]].

Immediately prior to and during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], this office was held by [[Armand Isard/Legends|Armand Isard]], who also held the position of [[Director of Republic Intelligence]].

In addition to the Director, the Bureau also had an [[Assistant Director/Legends|assistant director]].<ref name="MF">[[Millennium Falcon (novel)|''Millennium Falcon'']]</ref>

